# Formspree form endpoint ID
# 1. Go to https://formspree.io and create a free account
# 2. Create a new form — set the recipient email to your address
# 3. Copy the form ID from the URL (e.g. xpwzabcd) and paste it below
# 4. Copy this file to .env.local and fill in the value

VITE_FORMSPREE_ID=your_formspree_form_id_here
